name: The Nap of Time - Snorlax
description: UKTRA RARE - Along time ago in a universe run in 16 bit a snorlax Tokemon once at something that made him sick, not physically or anything like that. It sent him on a trip and that was that. The mushrooms smelt funny but he didnt care he ate them regarless of the warnings the other Tokemon shared, He now naps eternally struggling to break from the the horrible trip he didnt set out to see.
